* Straightforward installation

* No bloatware

* Updates are much more frequent than with CalyxOS on my old Fairphone 4.

* Fewer compatibility problems

  The user experience with the Google Play sandbox in GrapheneOS is _much_ better than with MicroG on CalyxOS.

